column4: Tweet on Altera-Intel talks came after options trades
column5: NEW YORK A March 27 tweet sent the same minute as news broke that chipmaker Intel Corp was in talks to buy Altera Corp appeared to come after very timely trades in Altera's options by several seconds  according to Thomson Reuters data.
